    <item>
      <title>美国国防部称中国加速核武器建设</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/china-speeds-nuclear-weapons-buildout-us-defense-agency-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美国最新的评估，中国正加紧推进迅速升级和扩大其陆、海、空核武器库的计划。这份评估对中国在落后领域追赶美国的努力提供了迄今为止最详细的说明。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/china-speeds-nuclear-weapons-buildout-us-defense-agency-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 20:08:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克政治行动委员会因向选民提供 100 万美元赠品而收到美国司法部警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/musk-pac-is-sent-doj-warning-for-1-million-voter-giveaway-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，美国司法部警告埃隆·马斯克的超级政治行动委员会，他提出的向美国摇摆州登记选民提供 100 万美元奖金的提议可能违反联邦法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/musk-pac-is-sent-doj-warning-for-1-million-voter-giveaway-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 19:56:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔毒枭被捕为诺沃亚带来急需的推动力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/arrest-of-top-ecuador-drug-lords-hands-noboa-much-needed-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瓜亚基尔电视台袭击案两名嫌疑人在西班牙被捕，此次袭击事件引起了全球关注，并引发了厄瓜多尔打击黑帮的战争，这给厄瓜多尔总统丹尼尔·诺沃亚在严重的电力危机中提供了急需的鼓舞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/arrest-of-top-ecuador-drug-lords-hands-noboa-much-needed-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 19:33:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多顶住了自由派议员的批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/trudeau-rides-out-criticism-from-anxious-liberal-lawmakers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多周三遭到了本党部分成员的猛烈批评，他们担心他的领导能力，但看来他面临的反对意见不足以迫使他下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/trudeau-rides-out-criticism-from-anxious-liberal-lawmakers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 19:31:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波士顿市长达成协议避免对房主征收 28% 的税款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/boston-mayor-strikes-deal-to-avoid-28-tax-hike-on-homeowners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿市长 Michelle Wu 与商界领袖达成妥协，以帮助推进一项旨在保护房主免受房产税大幅上涨影响的提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/boston-mayor-strikes-deal-to-avoid-28-tax-hike-on-homeowners</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 19:11:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市为移民提供资金以让他们离开，德克萨斯州是首选目的地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/nyc-is-paying-for-migrants-to-leave-and-texas-is-top-destination</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州已宣布已将 45,000 多名移民通过巴士送往纽约市。其中一些移民将直接返回。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/nyc-is-paying-for-migrants-to-leave-and-texas-is-top-destination</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 18:30:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙利文称拜登贸易限制有助于阻止另一场中国冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/biden-trade-curbs-helped-stop-another-china-shock-sullivan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在国际货币基金组织警告贸易壁垒对全球经济增长构成越来越大的风险之际，国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文为美国对国内产业的补贴和对中国的限制进行辩护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/biden-trade-curbs-helped-stop-another-china-shock-sullivan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 18:08:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼负责人称朝鲜军队已抵达俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/us-confirms-north-korean-troops-are-in-russia-to-back-its-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀称，朝鲜正在向俄罗斯派遣军队，这导致朝鲜军队被派往乌克兰作战的可能性“非常非常大”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/us-confirms-north-korean-troops-are-in-russia-to-back-its-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 14:04:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯会见沙特领导人，寻求缓解以以冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/us-diplomat-blinken-heads-to-saudi-arabia-after-urging-israel-to-ease-conflicts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登的高级外交官与沙特王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼举行会谈，讨论在加沙和黎巴嫩达成停火的努力，以争取地区支持推动和平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/us-diplomat-blinken-heads-to-saudi-arabia-after-urging-israel-to-ease-conflicts</guid>
